deps.context: find_package(hdf5 names ${hdf5_package_name} components c hl no_modules required static)

libs.content:
find_library ( xdr_libraries
  names xdr
  env xdr_root
  path_suffixes lib lib
  )

find_program (netcdf_ncdump_binary
	     name ncdump
	     paths
	       ${netcdf_binary_dir}
               ${netcdf_library_dirs}/../bin
               $env{access}/bin
               $env{netcdf_dir}/bin
               $env{netcdf_dir}/ncdump
               env path
	        ${netcdf_dir}/bin
	     )

find_library(
    fftw_lib
    names "fftw3"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwf_lib
    names "fftw3f"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwl_lib
    names "fftw3l"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(gsl_gsl_library
    names libgsl.dll.a gsl libgsl
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl library" )

find_library(gsl_gslcblas_library
    names libgslcblas.dll.a gslcblas libgslcblas
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl cblas library dir" )
